data.description:
Nestled in the highly sought after community of Canyon Trails is 8195 Half Dome Court, a gracious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in Boynton Beach that offers many features that make it ideal for family living. From the moment you pull into the brick driveway, you will feel you are at home. A long, landscaped path leads into a private covered entryway, which opens into a sizable 1,841 square foot living space with vaulted ceilings. From the kitchen to the bathrooms, to the patio and garage, the space has been completely renovated.  The entire space just feels clean and light thanks to a combination of thoughtful finishes like 36x36 white porcelain tiles and radiant natural light. A reimagined kitchen flows seamlessly into the spacious dining and living rooms, providing the perfect space to create lifetime memories with loved ones. The patio has now been extended and features brand new landscaping with turf in the backyard. 
 
Canyon Trails is in close proximity to A-rated schools and is close by to a brand-new middle school. The community features resort-style amenities like a fabulous pool, splash pad, playground, playroom, indoor sports court, tennis court, and basketball courts. 

The information published and provided including but not limited to prices, measurements, square footages, lot sizes, features, finishes, and calculations are subject to errors, omissions or changes without notice. All such information should be independently verified. All parties should perform their own due diligence to verify all information.
